title: metric: convert dash to underscore
body:
Fixes: https://github.com/vinted/elasticsearch-exporter-rs/issues/134

```
ERROR elasticsearch_exporter::collection                > GAUGE insert_gauge Metric("thread_pool_security-crypto_queue_size", Gauge(1000)) err Error: 'elasticsearch_nodes_info_thread_pool_security-crypto_queue_size' is not a valid metric name
```

Error happens due to `security-crypto` token returning key with dash which is not valid Prometheus metric.
